%% Diagram: Library Decision Tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
graph TD
    A[Need drag and drop] --> B{Cross-window drag<br/>or OS file drop?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Need native HTML5 DnD]
    C --> D[react-dnd<br/>or Pragmatic DnD<br/>or Sortable.js]
    B -->|No| G{Accessibility critical<br/>WCAG 2.2 AA?}
    G -->|Yes| H[React Aria DnD<br/>or dnd-kit<br/>or Pragmatic + a11y]
    G -->|Nice to have| K{Framework?}
    K -->|React| L[dnd-kit]
    K -->|Vanilla / other| O[Sortable.js<br/>or Pragmatic]
